{"tid":2264285,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"外交部汪：美國迫害人權 阻止逃犯自願返回中國自首","createTime":"2020-10-30T13:47:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-31T03:12:14.000Z","uid":337052,"like":5,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"49b74ba6769e835a390bd26bdf2dbc704d48bff9","tid":2264285,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T13:47:52.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">「獵狐行動」非法代理人被美國逮捕 中國政府切割了</span></strong><br />\n   <br />\n2020/10/30 17:16<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/10/30/phpDJbtF9.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F10%2F30%2FphpDJbtF9.jpg&d=e7N1rpd9%2BHLCKfTw7%2FjGdqHX%2F1llhPerIglyOgZNoj0%3D&h=a68b638f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F10%2F30%2FphpDJbtF9.jpg&h=4235b887\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/10/30/phpDJbtF9.jpg</a><br />\n汪文斌表示，美國逮捕的5名中國籍人士，與中國政府沒有關係。（法新社檔案照）<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕<span class=\"red\">美國司法部28日宣布起訴8名非法為中國執行「獵狐行動」的代理人，其中有5人當天上午在美國被捕，美方相信其他3人在中國。中國外交部發言人汪文斌今（30日）公開宣稱涉案人等與中國政府無關係。</span><br />\n<br />\n美國司法部公告，負責國家安全事務的助理部長德默斯（John C. Demers）表示，中國自2014年起進行被稱為「獵狐」的全球行動，中國官方稱這是一項國際反貪腐行動，但事實經常並非如此，被捕的是中共總書記習近平的政治對手、異見人士或批評者。<br />\n<br />\n德默斯表示，聯邦調查局（FBI）28日逮捕5名被告，他們被控在美國非法執行中國政府的指令，現在將面臨牢刑。尚有3人在逃，美方相信他們可能人在中國，這8人被控作為中國政府的非法代理人密謀在美國行事，其中6人還面臨共謀跨州和國際跟蹤相關指控。據稱，被告在中國官員的指示和控制下行事，監視、騷擾、跟踪和威脅美國某些居民返回中國。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/10/30/phpZTVJie.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F10%2F30%2FphpZTVJie.jpg&d=e7N1rpd9%2BHLCKfTw7%2FjGdqHX%2F1llhPerIglyOgZNoj0%3D&h=587cf7e1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F10%2F30%2FphpZTVJie.jpg&h=58b50de1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/10/30/phpZTVJie.jpg</a><br />\n美國司法部28日宣布起訴8名非法為中國執法「獵狐行動」的代理人。圖為司法部助理部長德默斯。（路透）<br />\n<br />\n根據中國《環球時報》報導，中國外交部發言人汪文斌今天宣稱：<span class=\"red\">「據我了解，美方最近逮捕的相關人員不是中方執法人員，其相關指控純屬造謠污衊。」</span>他認為，<span class=\"red\">「美國是中國外逃腐敗和經濟犯罪嫌疑人最集中的國家。但是近年來，美方一直消極對待中方提出的追逃等合作要求」，美執法部門甚至還「明目張膽為中方外逃嫌犯撐腰打氣、提供庇護」，阻撓外逃人員自願回國投案。</span><br />\n<br />\n汪文斌強調，美方的所作所為「完全站在了正義和法治的對立面」，中方認為此舉違背《聯合國反腐敗公約》和《聯合國打擊跨國有組織犯罪公約》精神，也背離美方在國際場合所做公開承諾。汪說：「我們要求美方停止無端指責抹黑中方的追逃追贓努力，切實履行國際義務和承諾，不要再貪圖嫌犯的黑錢，不要成為嫌犯和非法資產的避罪天堂。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3337003\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3337003&d=e7N1rpd9%2BHLCKfTw7%2FjGdqHX%2F1llhPerIglyOgZNoj0%3D&h=7b6fb815\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3337003&h=894ff4f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3337003</a>"},{"pid":"972775b3997689297d2f36865f22e69f8d76fe82","tid":2264285,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T13:49:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.justice.gov/opa/speech/assistant-attorney-general-john-c-demers-delivers-remarks-announcing-peoples-republic\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.justice.gov%2Fopa%2Fspeech%2Fassistant-attorney-general-john-c-demers-delivers-remarks-announcing-peoples-republic&d=e7N1rpd9%2BHLCKfTw7%2FjGdqHX%2F1llhPerIglyOgZNoj0%3D&h=0ff176a0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.justice.gov/opa/speech/assistant-attorney-general-john-c-demers-delivers-remarks-announcing-peoples-republic</a>"},{"pid":"ffa13dbfd6ee66651c2874729fabed2f7efe4a0b","tid":2264285,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T13:51:50.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">汪文斌公佈美逮捕參與&ldquo;獵狐行動&rdquo;有關人員進展：相關人員不是中方的執法人員</span></strong><br />\n來源：環球網作者：李司坤<br />\n<br />\n2020-10-30 16:01<br />\n<br />\n【環球時報-環球網報導記者李司坤】日前，美國司法部起訴並逮捕了涉嫌以中國非法代理人身份在美參與&ldquo;獵狐行動&rdquo;的有關人員，你昨天回答過有關問題，請問有沒有更多進展?你能否提供更多情況?<br />\n<br />\n答:我昨天已經闡明了中方立場。合作打擊包括腐敗在內的跨國犯罪、拒絕為犯罪嫌疑人和非法資金提供&ldquo;避罪天堂&rdquo;是國際社會共識，開展國際追逃追贓是維護和促進法治的正義事業。近年來，<span class=\"red\">我們先後與120多個國家和地區合作追回外逃嫌犯，合作中嚴格遵守國際法和國際司法執法慣例，充分尊重他國司法主權開展合作，依法保障犯罪嫌疑人合法權益，得到廣泛支持和充分肯定。</span><br />\n<br />\n據我了解，<span class=\"red\">美方最近逮捕的相關人員不是中方執法人員，其相關指控純屬造謠污衊。</span><br />\n<br />\n美國是中國外逃腐敗和經濟犯罪嫌疑人最集中的國家。但是近年來，美方一直消極對待中方提出的追逃等合作要求。<span class=\"red\">美國個別執法部門還明目張膽為中方外逃嫌犯撐腰打氣、提供庇護，並多次阻撓外逃人員自願回國投案。美方的所作所為完全站在了正義和法治的對立面</span>，違背了《聯合國反腐敗公約》和《聯合國打擊跨國有組織犯罪公約》精神，也背離了美方在國際場合所做公開承諾。我們要求美方停止無端指責抹黑中方的追逃追贓努力，切實履行國際義務和承諾，不要再貪圖嫌犯的黑錢，不要成為嫌犯和非法資產的&ldquo;避罪天堂&rdquo;。"},{"pid":"4a4e4c63ea6179757e03d37ee8c9ae79f24d330f","tid":2264285,"uid":186882,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T13:52:01.000Z","msg":"自首大國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d9aec42894bd2253757a02d4e75541bdce3c132","tid":2264285,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T13:52:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n汪汪汪"},{"pid":"5de84905bb83288d2a8a21f02b6fc29e31f6ad08","tid":2264285,"uid":49853,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T13:56:38.000Z","msg":"取消晒所有綠卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"522167fbb3b416f0a5f9ece4554b3b3b940a6167","tid":2264285,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a4e4c63ea6179757e03d37ee8c9ae79f24d330f","tid":2264285,"uid":186882,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T13:52:01.000Z","msg":"自首大國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T13:57:59.000Z","msg":"貪官罪犯外逃大國"},{"pid":"dda51086fc5b41c08dca98e17aad4d9809821b54","tid":2264285,"uid":203431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T14:14:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KSXzjUx.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKSXzjUx.gif&h=21e29e13&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d58b5350598ae4914a83edfdb87267c56b9c3c3f","tid":2264285,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T14:18:43.000Z","msg":"「獵狐行動」非法代理人被美國逮捕 中國政府切割了"},{"pid":"accaa37d93c5277b3d1c712ac1fe65f5dda625bd","tid":2264285,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T15:07:51.000Z","msg":"美執法部門甚至還「明目張膽為中方外逃嫌犯撐腰打氣、提供庇護」，阻撓外逃人員自願回國投案。"},{"pid":"0bf70268b871bc16070247bb89adb3c4b434c6e6","tid":2264285,"uid":28031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T15:42:24.000Z","msg":"比人用全家條命黎威脅果d重算唔算係「自願自首」？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b59ad7f1bdcfb5600d9adcef0d82728ba0327fc","tid":2264285,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T16:21:12.000Z","msg":"點解要當手足係CONDOM<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成日推人去送頭又無成效"},{"pid":"4c915ae691b38eaa2c875a5d214e9d7ad697ae36","tid":2264285,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T16:24:18.000Z","msg":"自願返回中國自首？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/47342/org/cd07868055abd37e99468fb8979ad5ae.png/jy55KtH2yMU7GfRx6p6WTGZenRvxnFomq18WYqtfFmI?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F47342%2Forg%2Fcd07868055abd37e99468fb8979ad5ae.png%2Fjy55KtH2yMU7GfRx6p6WTGZenRvxnFomq18WYqtfFmI%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=b6142fae&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"776807fe690792fa3bfbf0df556dd14d3b33e69d","tid":2264285,"uid":88848